      <bioghist id="aspace_fb23611d683663947931878f774b3735">
         <head>ALFRED STIEGLITZ AND GEORGIA O'KEEFFE</head>
         <p>Biographical statements can be found in the finding aid for the <ref actuate="onrequest"
                 href="http://hdl.handle.net/10079/fa/beinecke.sok"
                 show="new">Alfred Stieglitz / Georgia O'Keeffe Archive [YCAL MSS 85]</ref>.</p>  
      </bioghist>
      <scopecontent id="aspace_316d89ed66d429d945889d006b83c586">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>This collection gathers items related to Stieglitz and O'Keeffe which were acquired by the Beinecke Library after 1980. Earlier accessions are listed in the <ref actuate="onrequest"
                 href="http://hdl.handle.net/10079/fa/beinecke.sok"
                 show="new">Alfred Stieglitz / Georgia O'Keeffe Archive [YCAL MSS 85]</ref>. Materials incorporated into the collection prior to June 1997 have been organized into one series: <ref actuate="onrequest" show="replace" target="ref13">Correspondence</ref>. Materials added to the collection since that time are located in <ref actuate="onrequest" show="replace" target="ref33">Series II, Additions since June 1997</ref>, listed in the order in which they were added.</p>  
      </scopecontent>
